extends layout

block content
  h1 Transmogrify
  p Transmogrify is a small, fast image converter.
  h2 Try it!
  p Upload an SVG image here.
  form(action="/svg/png", method="post", enctype="multipart/form-data")
    input(type="file", name="svg")
    br
    input(name="width", value="600")
    label x
    input(name="height", value="400")
    br
    input(type="submit")
  p Or get all the SVGs from a given URL:
  form(action="/svg/page", method="post")
    input(name="url", value="http://www.jasondavies.com/animated-bezier/")
    input(type="submit")
